<bibRefCitation author="Rathbun" box="[722,885,626,650]" firstAuthor="Rathbun" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" pagination="1 - 24" refId="ref114279" refString="Rathbun, M. J. (1906) The Brachyura and Macrura of the Hawaiian Islands. Bulletin of the United States Fish Commission, 23 (3) [1903], 827 - 930, pls. 1 - 24." type="journal article" year="1906">Rathbun 1906</bibRefCitation>
